Nextel to Pick Huawei to Install Brazil 3G Network, Valor Says

-- B y   L a u r a   P r i c e
-- 
2011-02-15T08:52:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-15/nextel-to-pick-huawei-to-install-brazil-3g-network-valor-says.html
  NII Holdings Inc ., which operates
the Nextel brand in Latin America, plans to hire Huawei
Technologies Co. to install its third-generation mobile-phone
network in  Brazil , Valor Economico reported, citing unidentified
people close to the talks.  Nextel and Huawei are likely to announce the agreement
today, the Sao Paulo-based newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
